OL,3,CHigh-tech spoon developed to enrich
OL,4,Clives of dementia patients
OL,6,FThis can lead to patient's losing
OL,7,Fweight and muscle strength.
OL,9,FThe rechargeable Tasty Spoon looks
OL,10,Flike a traditional spoon but can help
OL,11,Fusers differentiate between types of
OL,12,Ffood, according to researchers.
OL,14,FIts development is being led by Dr
OL,15,FChristian Morgner, of the University
OL,16,Fof Sheffield's management school and
OL,17,FHealthy Lifespan Institute.
