OL,6,FAccording to the NHS, the total could
OL,7,Ftop one million people by 2030.
OL,9,FThe Tasty Spoon project has partnered
OL,10,Fwith Alzheimer's Society's Accelerator
OL,11,FProgramme, which is supporting
OL,12,Fbringing new products to market that
OL,13,Fhelp people living with dementia.
OL,15,FSimon Lord, head of innovation at
OL,16,FAlzheimer's Society, said: "A healthy,
OL,17,Fbalanced diet can help improve a
OL,18,Fperson's quality of life.
