OL,6,F"However, common symptoms of dementia,
OL,7,Fsuch as memory loss and difficulties
OL,8,Fwith thinking and problem-solving, can
OL,9,Fmake it more difficult to eat and
OL,10,Fdrink well.
OL,12,F"That's why we're excited about the
OL,13,Fpossibility Tasty Spoon presents in
OL,14,Fimproving the taste and enjoyment of
OL,15,Ffood and subsequently improving the
OL,16,Fhealth and nutrition of people living
OL,17,Fwith dementia.
