OL,6,F"Innovations like this are vital as
OL,7,Fthey focus on enriching daily
OL,8,Fexperiences and improving health and
OL,9,Fwell-being.
OL,11,F"Tasty Spoon is a unique product, and
OL,12,Fwe cannot wait to help get it into the
OL,13,Fhands of people living with dementia."
